title: DPS-BEST OF- Sep 08, 2020

description:
On today's episode of the Dan Patrick Show, we recap all that was in the weekend of sports. Could the BIG Ten go with 8 teams for a football season, DP has an update. NBC Sports Peter King joins the program. Plus, have the Cowboys cost themselves money by not extending Dak earlier? We discuss.
